@startuml cluster_warning_to_hud_warning_code_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Cluster Warning To HUD Warning Code Signal Flow\n(cluster warning + theme context -> HUD warning and brightness state)

participant "IVI / CLU warning source" as WarnSrc #F4F7FB
participant "Theme source" as ThemeSrc #E8F0FE
participant "HUD\nwarning-render owner" as HUD #E8F7E8
participant "HUD state bus" as HudBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nvisual readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== HUD Inputs ==

WarnSrc -> HUD : frmClusterWarningMsg\nWarningTextCode
ThemeSrc -> HUD : frmClusterThemeMsg\nThemeMode / ClusterBrightness
activate HUD
HUD -> HUD : warningInputExpired =\nethIsRecentTick(gWarningRxMs, 1500)
HUD -> HUD : themeInputExpired =\nethIsRecentTick(gThemeRxMs, 1500)
HUD -> HUD : if warning expired then\nwarningCode = 0
HUD -> HUD : if theme expired then\nthemeMode = 0 / brightness = 18
HUD -> HUD : hudMode = popup ? 2 :\nwarningCode > 0 ? 1 : guideType > 0 ? 3 : 0
HUD -> HUD : enforce minimum HUD brightness
note right of HUD
Representative gating inputs
- WarningTextCode
- ThemeMode
- ClusterBrightness
- HUD lease / hold windows
end note

== HUD Publish ==

HUD -> HudBus : frmHudStateMsg\nHudMode / HudWarningCode / HudBrightness
note right of HUD
Representative outputs
- HudMode
- HudWarningCode
- HudBrightness
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

HudBus -> Obs : HUD render visibility /\nwarning and theme observers
deactivate HUD

note over WarnSrc, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Cluster warning and theme context reach HUD
2. HUD applies lease/hold windows to warning and theme sources
3. HUD derives warning mode and final brightness
4. HUD publishes frmHudStateMsg for visual observers
end note

@enduml
